user.nickname: 三宝徒步西藏（黑龙江大庆）
user.signature:
2020年3🈷️31号
黑龙江省大庆市出发徒步西藏阿里冈仁波齐,全程7000公里。
黑龙江省➡️吉林省➡️内蒙古自治区➡️河北省➡️北京市➡️山西省➡️陕西省➡️四川省➡️西藏拉萨➡️（阿里冈仁波齐）磕大头绕山（三圈共165公里）
生活就像一场徒步旅行,穿越荆棘和沼泽,我们终将会迎来最美的风景。
⚠️小号：三宝徒步阿里（黑龙江大庆）

room.challenge_info: {"cid":"1583093219756045","cha_name":"刘耀文","desc":"刘耀文，2005年9月23日出生于重庆市，中国内地流行乐男歌手、演员，男子演唱组合时代少年团成员。\n2017年8月，参加TF家族夏日嘉年华  。2018年5月，参演的网络剧《念念》在腾讯视频上线首播 ；8月，随组合获得第三届粉丝嘉年华粉丝奖项“假奶协会终身名誉会员” ；10月，随组合举办出道首唱会，正式出道 。2019年2月，随组合登上2019年中央广播电视总台春节联欢晚会的舞台 ；4月，随组合为校园剧《你好，对方辩友》演唱主题曲；8月，台风少年蜕变之战落幕，刘耀文成功加入组合时代少年团 {"cid":"1572072504832002","cha_name":"王一博","desc":"王一博，中国内地男歌手、演员、职业摩托车赛车手，1997年8月5日出生于河南洛阳。2014年9月15日，作为UNIQ组合成员出道，2016年4月加入《天天向上》。第30届中国电视金鹰奖观众喜爱的男演员。《陪你到世界之巅》饰季向空，《陈情令》饰蓝忘机，《有翡》饰谢允，《冰雨火》饰陈宇，《风起洛阳》饰百里弘毅。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1572072504832002","author":{"uid":"101562100101","short_id":"2014940272","nickname":"王一博吧_WYBBar","gender":1,"signature":"王一博是最酷的盖","avatar_larger":{"uri":"1080x1080/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866","url_list":["https://p29.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_1080x1080.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_1080x1080.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_1080x1080.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866","url_list":["https://p29.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_100x100.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_100x100.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_100x100.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"720x720/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_720x720.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_720x720.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p6.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_720x720.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":true,"constellation":10,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_ver user.nickname: 达子gg (带着琴宝徒步穿越西藏)
user.signature:
2019.10月2号至2020.6月15号从湖北宜昌北山坡出发.拉500斤车徒步西藏成功。
一生要去两次西藏，第一次把心留在了那里，第二次找回来。
今年2021年3月底从成都出发，和琴宝两人徒步318川藏线，预计9月中抵达拉萨，然后往日喀则，阿里方向出发，在走109青藏线回(注:抵达拉萨后 根据琴宝身体状况选择走或停留)

{"cid":"1661986683079688","cha_name":"大话西游直播","desc":"至尊宝（周星驰饰）被月光宝盒带回到五百年前，遇见紫霞仙子（朱茵饰），被对方打上烙印成为了对方的人，并发觉自己已变成孙悟空。\n紫霞与青霞（朱茵饰）本是如来佛祖座前日月神灯的灯芯（白天是紫霞，晚上是青霞），二人虽然同一肉身却仇恨颇深，因此紫霞立下誓言，谁能拔出她手中的紫青宝剑，谁就是她的意中人。\n紫青宝剑被至尊宝于不经意间拔出，紫霞决定以身相许，却遭一心记挂白晶晶（莫文蔚饰）的至尊宝拒绝。后牛魔王（陆树铭饰）救下迷失在沙漠中的紫霞，并逼紫霞与他成婚，关键时刻，至尊宝现身。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1661986683079688","author":{"uid":"6796248446","short_id":"52","nickname":"抖音小助手","gender":1,"signature":"本宝宝暂时还没想到个性签名","avatar_larger":{"uri":"1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p26.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p26.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":true,"constellation":10,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_verify":"","unique_id":"douyin","bind_phone":"","special_lock":0,"need_recommend":0,"is_binded_weibo":false,"weibo_name":"","weibo_schema":"","weibo_url":"","story_open":false,"story_count":0,"has_facebook_token":false,"has_twitter_token
